# Trivy ignore list for the mochi-server Docker image.
#
# Add a CVE id (one per line) to suppress findings that are accepted —
# typically because the fix is upstream-blocked and we're waiting on a
# distribution to ship it. Each entry should carry a comment explaining
# why and a date to re-evaluate.

# CVE-2026-0861 — glibc memalign integer overflow leading to heap
# corruption. Distroless cc-debian12 inherits libc6 from Debian 12; no
# fix available upstream as of 2026-05. Re-evaluate when Debian ships a
# glibc 2.36 patch.
CVE-2026-0861
